name: Non Fungible Unicorn
description: A unicorn collection with different elements
abi: constructor(string name, string symbol, string baseURI, string description, address royaltyReceiver, uint96 royaltyFeeBps)
function getCollectionInfo() view returns (string, string, string, uint256, address, address, uint96)
function royaltyInfo(uint256 tokenId, uint256 salePrice) view returns (address, uint256)

event Transfer(address indexed from, address indexed to, uint256 indexed tokenId)
